{"tid":137851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]恐怖工業意外　工人捲破碎機當場慘死","createTime":"2017-02-28T06:45:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T06:47:10.000Z","uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f17995554f0031a9210ab9da0e0a01c4c4fbc7f","tid":137851,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:45:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170227/bkncn-20170227230028186-0227_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170227%2Fbkncn-20170227230028186-0227_05011_001.html&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=b9be52d7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170227/bkncn-20170227230028186-0227_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170227/photo/bkncn-20170227230028186-0227_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170227%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170227230028186-0227_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=dcc34610&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n福建泉州市惠安縣一間塑料公司昨日發生恐怖工業意外。一名男工人上半身被捲入工廠的破碎機內，消防員將他救出後，證實其當場身亡。目前事故原因仍有待進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n據工友表示，該廠以生產即棄快餐盒為主，死者姓黃，安徽人，是工廠的老員工。他表示，事發時剛好路過廠房，由於當時正值上班時間，但發現機器沒有聲音，便下意識地看了一眼，赫見有人被卡住，遂立即報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n在救援人員趕抵現場前，工人們曾試圖營救，但未能成功。消防、警察及急救人員其後趕抵現場，消防要先將破碎機拆開，才能將被困工人救出，並交由現場的醫護人員急救。惟經檢查後，證實該名工人已當場身亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b3c1cb9e65ac270c0e452b5c46412ffcecf2b29","tid":137851,"uid":61210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T06:47:10.000Z","msg":"做乜學亞人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}